headline: DTE Energy: An Undervalued Utility Stock For Long-Term Dividend Growth Investors
summary: DTE Energy has increased its dividend for 16 consecutive years. Its 10-year dividend growth rate of 7.3% is strong. See why I rate DTE stock a buy.
